{"h47cf6897gfb0fg4dabgaf2agdb8e6f9c69d3": ["Chosen.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "0f31d45c-073f-5446-0b1e-2fca2b4ae5be"], "hddaed753g1a2bg4374gaa23g8d5691f71546": ["Let me come to you. I can help you.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "0f378160-7e12-e509-82a6-45c59361f7b3"], "he5dd5ac6g8c6bg46cbg9d14g30aba7a60211": ["I know your voice. I heard it on the nautiloid.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "30add8f6-83e5-4ceb-f169-ce2303c82bcd"], "h1d844373ge17cg46c8ga9acg8a1180cc7cba": ["I've been searching for you. You're always so far away.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "121c9bcf-b7fa-d9f6-a35f-fdefdad8816f"], "h51b31d91g5da8g460cg8a10g6cf2836b9b9b": ["Come here. Come to me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "f91523cc-e6da-4c43-943d-ca64b483b050"], "h3a1dcfbeg8bd0g4a84g95d7gc735575ee3d0": ["You frown in your sleep.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "b2eb3928-e3dd-d854-06f9-087e19652088"], "h5e4eb985g450bg4666ga81dg78169c8f244b": ["There must be so much on your mind.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "5ba1c06a-cc01-b9c3-30ee-7bc62de2664f"], "ha22defa0gfec7g4368gaed1g0c6661689853": ["*Her fingers are warm against your cheek, softer than expected.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "0c7332d4-6b81-7182-9001-df78a0f011dd"], "h1418e9eag3526g4e93g9ed2g79a64a6b1949": ["*His fingers are warm against your cheek, softer than expected.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "0c7332d4-6b81-7182-9001-df78a0f011dd"], "h1d5926b1g1265g49abg8883g32bf7363c288": ["You think that you're sick. That you're dying.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "6da08b28-8a88-ebde-e3e3-084c6a8e32ca"], "hf3f048a0gadb7g4b8fg817bgcb0776861f81": ["Are you afraid?", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "58b64c48-d47b-c380-100f-7c42d41b87e1"], "h262f3665gf6adg42ccga6a0g0481f81ece8d": ["Who are you - <i>what</i> are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "f79de8ed-9786-c359-f84c-a83b913f3700"], "hb36bb329g1459g4b4eg90c7gdb99fc1fc16c": ["You know. I think in your heart, you know.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "1a0b42e4-95fe-578c-8aee-de30760f7632"], "h29521ac6g3d7fg4862g9235g7976123ae6c2": ["We wouldn't be here like this if it weren't destiny.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "8319bb91-179c-4ece-e489-150a6c2e4da4"], "h915498b8g45acg4148g9985gd4e93b171489": ["Come now. I'll make you feel better.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "13e95a73-99d5-4b8e-7719-aa1d357512aa"], "h5a71eb6agd371g4825ga8e1gdf1f3ab33739": ["Let yourself go. Lean back.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "f359b875-cae2-0182-b37d-640f9be09fd8"], "h1ba5efcdg73cfg4ff6ga854g776123ee6b5a": ["<i>Do as she says.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "75058f1c-2c64-ddcf-ca11-1c2a1e0c5b3c"], "h7fca01c9g03f4g445bga7b8g5ccb83cf5c9c": ["<i>Do as he says.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "75058f1c-2c64-ddcf-ca11-1c2a1e0c5b3c"], "h3d352d70g7649g4637g91e7g86054c7e1724": ["So eager. Hungry. But...", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "d57196dc-b4c5-b7ec-8115-946483f3bd8e"], "h717e8fdfgec9bg4790gb80eg86a2eac33527": ["*Something in your blood stirs and twists, recoiling like a wounded beast. It wants her gone.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "fdb46579-1ac7-2733-ec5f-76398227fce8"], "hcd042db4g58bfg42cdg930fgdd40e3bfae97": ["*Something in your blood stirs and twists, recoiling like a wounded beast. It wants him gone.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "fdb46579-1ac7-2733-ec5f-76398227fce8"], "h80246353ge1f9g46a5gb629gd30efcf192e4": ["...you're not ready.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "e0bf96d5-4030-f5ab-3cc6-c0538b286eb5"], "h12f38420g76a7g4c0fg9895gb987fc0364ab": ["I will return when you are.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "90fdd305-c2a1-6368-acc2-0dcf11247140"], "he8be5da0g8b8cg49a4gaa7eg7e9a4c5cf23b": ["But I do have a parting gift...", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "92b0ad3f-f44b-e09c-98c4-0af27ea3b892"], "h45ef0be8gb727g481fg863bg2a6b058877e9": ["<i>Resist. Force her away.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "ccf19d56-8db9-5b6d-54b7-f2145081ab47"], "hf5cd6be9gb59eg41aag8cb2g940517e60739": ["<i>Resist. Force him away.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "ccf19d56-8db9-5b6d-54b7-f2145081ab47"], "h65856084g1348g4ec0gbd18g978da76caab0": ["Why are you fighting me? I'm here to help you.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "58e739e6-2c57-6512-d543-bf5e260a5978"], "ha3579e5age41bg4608g899bg5c523eb58f8c": ["*The urge for violence lingers. You could push her again. You could cause so much pain.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "62ee227c-9565-39e3-32b3-d35de07585d8"], "h2d11b55cgd3f6g47edg8fa7gb20c1c5f844f": ["*The urge for violence lingers. You could push him again. You could cause so much pain.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "62ee227c-9565-39e3-32b3-d35de07585d8"], "hcaa1cd41g8ceeg4e36gae22gf62ef4f58ac1": ["Well, if you want to wait, I'll wait.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "926520ab-df11-ba75-fdee-d8c4df82fe6f"], "h9bbebd02ga265g47aag8d80g2f577b1ecd25": ["<i>Stay silent.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "52eb948a-f5db-c87c-1412-928b4ccab6a1"], "hbe0f5f61g9886g48eaga66cgfa53345d366f": ["Touch me again and I'll split you open!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "319a8a12-5fb2-7cd9-c79a-4b1347aa80c0"], "h20957e66g52fcg4201gb85dgf3bc497b0bb7": ["Back off! Touch me again and I'll bleed you dry.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "319a8a12-5fb2-7cd9-c79a-4b1347aa80c0"], "h0262aef0g9430g484cg9cc6g871ef47e2602": ["Is that so?", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "7f1b77ed-8f5f-f642-fc8b-06f0929250c1"], "h410d8827g8247g4379ga0abg8be2cb6afeb1": ["Perhaps you prefer a different kind of touch.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "6369f9a3-4693-1cdd-445d-06a675ca7bd9"], "h8ec9fd9egc7ebg4cecg8aa5gac40bf3266a8": ["I was afraid. Then I saw you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "b88e544f-8084-8a8f-5de4-f2b5b42874d5"], "hba752611gc082g4479g85ccge11fb61ebe58": ["Look at you. So confused, brimming with power.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "c5c29f78-a1ca-cdab-27c6-a74c6726d933"], "hc36059b9gb771g4dfbgb653g19514b1291c7": ["Yet still a shadow of what you will become.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "003d664c-f63d-8755-aab1-623fe6122ab6"], "hef5970b8ga8dfg4f66g8864g35a678db9a61": ["I am turning into my people's worst foe. There is no greater failure.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "19695f17-0675-2de6-53b8-f1b3fad2837c"], "h59f5af9ag89afg4c66g9f65gec185d84e3f2": ["I'm one bad turn from becoming a mind flayer.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "19695f17-0675-2de6-53b8-f1b3fad2837c"], "hd4b3ab2ag72d5g43c0g821ag6842d2c42a22": ["You don't understand, darling. You're turning, yes, but...", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "f28f0516-2029-22eb-3d34-78474187ab87"], "h4dcd6661g7c81g464cgb246g58826f931527": ["I fear nothing. I'll purge this sickness and be free again.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "4c921229-f2be-aa8a-7b63-1ca0f2741a12"], "h581701e0g8b3eg460cgbf93g946f86ed6e4b": ["You're so close to power. Right on the cusp.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "a0218cb7-39af-9fc3-b3d0-f3928f26fdfb"], "hd048afe5gad79g4e16ga383g2dfcde597a5c": ["I never <i>sleep</i>. How is this possible?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "a8851c99-673b-df2c-9c51-ec288682893e"], "h9d1f43bfgd8aag4e09gabbeg1d79d511030a": ["How far does the deepest trance lay from sleep?", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "1eca8bde-f0ff-6690-6ecd-851fb846cfee"], "h77a87d65g5979g4ce4gab7cg6b2ca3cb8122": ["I leave that answer to your clever mind, darling.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "dbe450ba-c0d0-8c83-4e4a-c6b13b5371e0"], "h4c99667agc975g4c70ga6c6gae54df6ae5f7": ["Am I... asleep? Like a creature of flesh?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "7b6b6ce5-f0e2-cd53-1e49-578bffc5e7c6"], "h2f2c7376gc311g4cdfgb246ga00c96b032e0": ["Revel in the sensation. ", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "f2ed865d-92f3-e242-3c28-5fdfb4e06a66"], "h439d450cg9955g4e0ega217g78bc53044397": ["The flesh has so much to offer.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "8f869905-16db-f962-651b-a7d714b314dd"], "h2e81da86ge55ag4125g8028g37e3a6b7f731": ["This is <i>ghaik</i> trickery. I will not bow to your summons!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "fe234438-905a-4e76-ff40-4f321c2da894"], "h78115efbg6a80g4088g8272g22b4b1770654": ["Back off. I have enough crawling around in my head.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "fe234438-905a-4e76-ff40-4f321c2da894"], "hc0b7f094g90f9g4c54gb366gfae60ba96589": ["But I'm already here.", "6fe77279-1bba-5cc0-a5e0-34beabd2501d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_Daisy1_AvD_ROM.html", "3a2159e8-3110-2201-ab9c-13ec92c72fe4"]}